## Pre-Deploy Validation

Before creating or approving any deploy-related PR, run the pre-deployment validation script:

```bash
python3 backend/scripts/pre_deploy_check.py --live
```

This ensures:
- The backend API imports correctly
- All tests pass
- Static files serve correctly
- Documentation is up to date with code
- Environment variables are properly configured
- The health endpoint responds as expected

If the script exits with a non-zero status, investigate and fix the failures before proceeding with the deployment.